# apps/edpath-web — Next.js + CopilotKit

- This is NOT the Next.js you may know — read the in-repo guide referenced by `apps/edpath-web/AGENTS.md` before writing code.
- Render from mirrored agent state. The client holds NO progress/score state (only `threadId`). See `docs/reference/feature-flow.md` Part C §1 and `docs/reference/architecture.md` §5 (the CopilotKit bridge).
- Send intents only — approval decision, selected option index, free-text help. No business logic, no grading, no LLM calls client-side.
- Green/red are functional feedback states, not styling.
